highlights.text: “Grama Verde” by Filipe Ret and Prod.MTS is the highest new entry on Top Songs Brazil at #72.
“Lapada Dela - Ao Vivo” by Grupo Menos É Mais and Matheus Fernandes has been on Top Songs Brazil the longest, at 869 days straight.
Henrique & Juliano has the most spots on Top Songs Brazil. “Última Saudade - Ao Vivo” is the highest at #11.
“Nós Combina” by Mãolee, Filipe Ret, and Vulgo FK is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Brazil, up 92 spots at #91.
